he name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]},{"name":"Frances","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Feminine form of   Francis .  In the 16th century the two spellings were used indiscriminately for both sexes, the distinction in spelling not being established until the 17th century."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Elizabeth Frances Kellaway was born in 1525, in Nayland, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom, her father, John Kelleway, was 31 and her mother, Joan Tregarthen, was 34. She had at least 1 daughter with John Plampin. She died about 1560, in her hometown, at the age of 36."},"et":{"1525–abt 1560":"1525–umbes 1560","1525–1560":"1525–1560","1525–1563":"1525–1563","1560–1618":"1560–1618","1494–Male":"1494–Surnud","1492–1583":"1492–1583","1525":"1525","1563":"1563","1583":"1583","1494":"1494","1560":"1560","abt 1560":"umbes 1560","1492":"1492","1618":"1618","about 1560":"umbes 1560","Nayland, Suffolk, England":"Nayland, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Essex, England":"Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1525–abt 1560":"1525–noin 1560","1525–1560":"1525–1560","1525–1563":"1525–1563","1560–1618":"1560–1618","1494–Male":"1494–Kuollut","1492–1583":"1492–1583","1525":"1525","1563":"1563","1583":"1583","1494":"1494","1560":"1560","abt 1560":"noin 1560","1492":"1492","1618":"1618","about 1560":"noin 1560","Nayland, Suffolk, England":"Nayland, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Essex, England":"Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1525–abt 1560":"1525–environ 1560","1525–1560":"1525–1560","1525–1563":"1525–1563","1560–1618":"1560–1618","1494–Male":"1494–Décédé","1492–1583":"1492–1583","1525":"1525","1563":"1563","1583":"1583","1494":"1494","1560":"1560","abt 1560":"environ 1560","1492":"1492","1618":"1618","about 1560"